title: FortiGate Firewall Cluster Monitoring: Sync Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the synchronization status of a FortiGate High-Availability cluster. The status 'synchronized' is considered OK and the status 'unsynchronized' CRIT.

inventory:
 One service is created for each cluster (master and slave node).
 No service is created for standalone firewall (only  master node).
